source: crates/franken-node/tests/cli_subcommand_goldens.rs
---
Remote capability token issuance and inspection

Usage: franken-node remotecap <COMMAND>

Commands:
  issue   Issue a signed capability token for network-bound operations
  verify  Verify a capability token without consuming single-use tokens
  use     Use a capability token for one network-bound operation
  revoke  Revoke a capability token in the local CLI state
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
